00:40:16,800 --> 00:40:17,840
Here.

474
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:20,960
I'm all right.

475
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:29,720
[panting]

476
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:49,840
You see me as I am.

477
00:40:53,520 --> 00:40:54,360
