478
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:58,480
You don't see roach?

479
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:01,360
You ain't a roach.

480
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:04,320
Roaches is all...

481
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:07,400
Fucked up?

482
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,080
